  "id": "guide/i18n-common",
  "title": "Common Internationalization tasks",
  "contents": "\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-common.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"common-internationalization-tasks\" translation-result=\"on\">常见的国际化任务<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common#common-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"common-internationalization-tasks\">Common Internationalization tasks<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common#common-internationalization-tasks\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用 Angular 让你的应用程序国际化</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use Angular to internationalize your application</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用内置管道以本地格式显示日期、数字、百分比和货币。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use built-in pipes to display dates, numbers, percentages, and currencies in a local format.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在组件模板中标记文本以进行翻译。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Mark text in component templates for translation.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">标记复数形式的表达式以供翻译。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Mark plural forms of expressions for translation.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">标记替代文本以进行翻译。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Mark alternate text for translation.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在为国际受众准备应用程序后，使用 <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 来本地化你的应用程序。完成以下任务以本地化你的应用程序。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">After you prepare your application for an international audience, use the <a href=\"cli\" title=\"CLI Overview and Command Reference | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> to localize your application.\nComplete the following tasks to localize your application.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用 CLI 将标记的文本提取到<em>源语言</em>文件中。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the CLI to extract marked text to a <em>source language</em> file.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">为每种语言制作此文件的副本，并将这些<em>翻译文件</em>发送给翻译人员或服务。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Make a copy of this file for each language, and send these <em>translation files</em> to a translator or service.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在为一种或多种语言环境构建应用程序时，使用 CLI 合并完成的翻译文件。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the CLI to merge the finished translation files when building your application for one or more locales.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要浏览本指南中使用的法语翻译示例应用程序，请参阅<live-example></live-example> 。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To explore the sample application with French translations used in this guide, see <live-example></live-example>.</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" translation-result=\"on\">前提条件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"prerequisites\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在准备翻译你的应用之前，你应该对以下主题有基本的了解。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To prepare your application for translations, you should have a basic understanding of the following subjects.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">模板</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\" title=\"template - Glossary | Angular\">Templates</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">组件</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#component\" title=\"component - Glossary | Angular\">Components</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> 用于管理 Angular 开发周期的命令行工具</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\" title=\"command-line interface (CLI) - Glossary | Angular\">Angular CLI</a> command-line tool for managing the Angular development cycle</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">Extensible Markup Language (XML)</a> 用于翻译文件</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/XML\" title=\"Extensible Markup Language (XML) | W3C\">Extensible Markup Language (XML)</a> used for translation files</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"steps-to-localize-your-app\" translation-result=\"on\">本地化应用程序的步骤<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common#steps-to-localize-your-app\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"steps-to-localize-your-app\">Steps to localize your app<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common#steps-to-localize-your-app\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要本地化你的应用程序，请完成以下常规操作。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To localize your application, complete the following general actions.</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package\" title=\"Common Internationalization task #1: Add the localize package | Angular\">添加本地化包</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package\" title=\"Common Internationalization task #1: Add the localize package | Angular\">Add the localize package</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\" title=\"Refer to locales by ID | Angular\">通过 ID 引用语言环境</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-locale-id\" title=\"Refer to locales by ID | Angular\">Refer to locales by ID</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\" title=\"Format data based on locale | Angular\">根据语言环境格式化数据</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\" title=\"Format data based on locale | Angular\">Format data based on locale</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-prepare\" title=\"Prepare templates for translations | Angular\">准备翻译模板</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-prepare\" title=\"Prepare templates for translations | Angular\">Prepare templates for translations</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-translation-files\" title=\"Work with translation files | Angular\">使用翻译文件</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-translation-files\" title=\"Work with translation files | Angular\">Work with translation files</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-merge\" title=\"Merge translations into the application | Angular\">将翻译合并到应用程序中</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-merge\" title=\"Merge translations into the application | Angular\">Merge translations into the app</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-deploy\" title=\"Deploy multiple locales | Angular\">部署多个语言环境</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-common-deploy\" title=\"Deploy multiple locales | Angular\">Deploy multiple locales</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">当你按照操作进行操作时，<a href=\"guide/i18n-example\" title=\"Example Angular application: Explore the translated example application | Angular\">浏览已翻译的示例应用程序</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">While you follow the actions, <a href=\"guide/i18n-example\" title=\"Example Angular application: Explore the translated example application | Angular\">explore the translated example app</a>.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在特殊情况下，需要执行以下操作。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In special cases, the following actions are required.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果你需要设置 <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\">LOCALE_ID</a> 令牌，请<a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale\" title=\"Set the source locale manually | Angular\">手动设置源语言环境</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale\" title=\"Set the source locale manually | Angular\">Set the source locale manually</a>, if you need to set the <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\">LOCALE_ID</a> token.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\" title=\"Import global variants of the locale data | Angular\">导入语言环境数据的全局变量</a> 以获得额外的语言环境数据。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\" title=\"Import global variants of the locale data | Angular\">Import global variants of the locale data</a> for extra locale data.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果你需要对匹配翻译进行更多控制，请<a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\" title=\"Manage marked text with custom IDs | Angular\">使用自定义 ID 管理标记文本</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\" title=\"Manage marked text with custom IDs | Angular\">Manage marked text with custom IDs</a>, if you require more control over matching translations.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- externla links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间： 2021/9/15</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - cli\n - guide/glossary#command-line-interface-cli\n - guide/glossary#component\n - guide/glossary#template\n - guide/i18n-common#common-internationalization-tasks\n - guide/i18n-common#prerequisites\n - guide/i18n-common#steps-to-localize-your-app\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package\n - guide/i18n-common-deploy\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - guide/i18n-common-merge\n - guide/i18n-common-prepare\n - guide/i18n-common-translation-files\n - guide/i18n-example\n - guide/i18n-optional-import-global-variants\n - guide/i18n-optional-manage-marked-text\n - guide/i18n-optional-manual-source-locale\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-common.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n - https://www.w3.org/XML\n-->"
